  "detailed_description": "\"MOMIJI FROM PURGATORY\" is a horror adventure game that is played entirely from the first-person perspective, the player will take control of a college boy who is exposed for his cheating and is subsequently pursued by a series of plans for love.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1647240/extras/ce06e188a0d17410d07d9eba62414d75.avif?t=1753685373\" width=650 height=370 /></span><br>Stepping into this campus with a weird atmosphere and traps everywhere, just to rescue true love.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1647240/extras/c34b738a4c0641026496b8ca0685cb9f.avif?t=1753685373\" width=650 height=370 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1647240/extras/6e9b4f222a9eedd3f443d4163186ea2a.avif?t=1753685373\" width=650 height=370 /></span><br>On the way to the rescue, player will encounter harassment from many disgusting fans.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1647240/extras/b75ffaf2577f55568ff5b84f78e6cae7.avif?t=1753685373\" width=650 height=370 /></span><br>In the end, the boss will make the protagonist and his lover pay the price at all costs...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1647240/extras/fa5eca333dbd632cc8a5c9aa5cc75356.avif?t=1753685373\" width=650 height=370 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "\"MOMIJI FROM PURGATORY\" is a horror adventure game that is played entirely from the first-person perspective, the player will take control of a college boy who is exposed for his cheating and is subsequently pursued by a series of plans for love.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1647240/extras/ce06e188a0d17410d07d9eba62414d75.avif?t=1753685373\" width=650 height=370 /></span><br>Stepping into this campus with a weird atmosphere and traps everywhere, just to rescue true love.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1647240/extras/c34b738a4c0641026496b8ca0685cb9f.avif?t=1753685373\" width=650 height=370 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1647240/extras/6e9b4f222a9eedd3f443d4163186ea2a.avif?t=1753685373\" width=650 height=370 /></span><br>On the way to the rescue, player will encounter harassment from many disgusting fans.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1647240/extras/b75ffaf2577f55568ff5b84f78e6cae7.avif?t=1753685373\" width=650 height=370 /></span><br>In the end, the boss will make the protagonist and his lover pay the price at all costs...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1647240/extras/fa5eca333dbd632cc8a5c9aa5cc75356.avif?t=1753685373\" width=650 height=370 /></span>",
